'''二氢硫辛酰胺脱氢酶'''（{{EC|1.8.1.4}}，{{lang-en|Dihydrolipoamide dehydrogenase}}，缩写'''DLD'''，又称为'''线粒体二氢硫辛酸脱氢酶'''，{{lang|en|dihydrolipoyl dehydrogenase, mitochondrial}}）是一种由人类基因''DLD''<ref name="entrez">{{cite web| title = Entrez Gene: dihydrolipoamide dehydrogenase| url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=gene&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=1738| accessdate = | archive-date = 2010-03-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100306223724/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=gene&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=1738| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="pmid3693355">{{cite journal | author = Otulakowski G, Robinson BH | title = Isolation and sequence determination of cDNA clones for porcine and human lipoamide dehydrogenase. Homology to other disulfide oxidoreductases | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 262 | issue = 36 | pages = 17313–8 |date=December 1987 | pmid = 3693355 | doi = | url = | issn = }}</ref><ref name="pmid3278312">{{cite journal | author = Pons G, Raefsky-Estrin C, Carothers DJ, Pepin RA, Javed AA, Jesse BW, Ganapathi MK, Samols D, Patel MS | title = Cloning and cDNA sequence of the dihydrolipoamide dehydrogenase component human alpha-ketoacid dehydrogenase complexes | journal = Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. | volume = 85 | issue = 5 | pages = 1422–6 |date=March 1988 | pmid = 3278312 | pmc = 279783 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.85.5.1422| url = | issn = }}</ref><ref name="pmid2055113">{{cite journal | author = Scherer SW, Otulakowski G, Robinson BH, Tsui LC | title = Localization of the human dihydrolipoamide dehydrogenase gene (DLD) to 7q31----q32 | journal = Cytogenet. Cell Genet. | volume = 56 | issue = 3-4 | pages = 176–7 | year = 1991 | pmid = 2055113 | doi = 10.1159/000133081| url = | issn = }}</ref>所编码的[[黄素蛋白|黄素蛋白]]，其作用是将[[二氢硫辛酰胺|二氢硫辛酰胺]]脱氢从而转化为氧化型[[硫辛酰胺|硫辛酰胺]]。

DLD作为一种线粒体蛋白质，在真核生物的能量代谢中起到重要作用，它至少参与了五种[[多酶复合体|多酶复合体]]，且为复合体完成反应所必需的组份<ref name="Babady">{{cite journal | author = Babady NE, Pang YP, Elpeleg O, Isaya G | title = Cryptic proteolytic activity of dihydrolipoamide dehydrogenase | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 104 | issue = 15 | pages = 6158–63 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17404228 | pmc = 1851069 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.0610618104 }}</ref>。另外，DLD作为一种[[黄素蛋白|黄素蛋白]][[氧化還原酶|氧化還原酶]]，以[[黄素腺嘌呤二核苷酸|FAD]]为辅基接受质子与电子催化[[二硫键|二硫键]]的形成。

DLD是大小为51千道尔顿亚基的同二聚体，其中每个亚基都与一分子的[[黄素腺嘌呤二核苷酸|FAD]]以共价键的形式相连<ref name="Ciszak">{{cite journal | author = Ciszak EM, Makal A, Hong YS, Vettaikkorumakankauv AK, Korotchkina LG, Patel MS | title = How dihydrolipoamide dehydrogenase-binding protein binds dihydrolipoamide dehydrogenase in the human pyruvate dehydrogenase complex | journal = The Journal of Biological Chemistry | volume = 281 | issue = 1 | pages = 648–55 | year = 2006  | pmid = 16263718 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.M507850200 | url = }}</ref>。
